ABOUT

KING is tired of watching everyone play hot potato with the endless derivative ShibaCumGMElonKishuPepeTurboAssFlokiMoon Inu coins. The Dog’s and Frog’s have had their day. It’s time for the king to take his reign as the king of this jungle of memes.
King is not here to make meme coin great again because King is already great. King is here to remind everyone that he is the King. Launched stealth with no presale, zero taxes, LP burnt and contract renounced. What is better than 93.1% tokens to liquidity pool, it is 100% going to liquidity pool. Can you beat it? Fueled by pure king power, let $KING show you the way.

HOW TO BUY

Create a Wallet

download metamask or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktop users, download the google chrome extension by going to metamask.io.

Get Some WPLS

have WPLS in your wallet to switch to $KING. If you don’t have any WPLS, you can buy directly on metamask, transfer from another wallet, or buy on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

Go to 9inch

connect to 9inch. Go to app.9inch.io in google chrome or on the browser inside your Metamask app. Connect your wallet. Paste the $KING token address into 9inch, select KING, and confirm. When Metamask prompts you for a wallet signature, sign.

Swap WPLS for $KING

Swap WPLS for $KING. We have ZERO taxes so you don’t need to worry about buying with a specific slippage, although you may need to use slippage during times of market volatility.
